I have an Example that contains a bunch of `bytes_list` values. I dropped a debugger in [this function](https://github.com/spotify/spotify-tensorflow/blob/d2f093d355a2caa67c1e1566b6b50f4fe4d478f9/spotify_tensorflow/example_decoders.py#L29-L40) and inspected the data.

Looking at the example `ex`, I see

```
feature {
    key: "genres"
    value {
      bytes_list {
        value: "country"
        value: "modern country rock"
      }
    }
  }
```

Looking at it after `MessageToJson`, and also what prints to the console when using `tfr-read`, I see:

```
      "microgenre_affinity.genres": {
        "bytesList": {
          "value": [
            "Y291bnRyeQ==",
            "bW9kZXJuIGNvdW50cnkgcm9jaw==",
          ]
```
